definitions.definition: A department of Picardy , Hauts-de-France , France . Capital: Beauvais ( INSEE code 60).
A right tributary of the Seine , originating in Belgium and flowing through the departments of Aisne , Oise , Val-d'Oise and Yvelines in northeastern France .
